<template>
  <a-scene
    arjs
    embedded
    @markerFound="find()"
    @markerLost="lost()"
    gltf-model="dracoDecoderPath: https://www.gstatic.com/draco/versioned/decoders/1.4.1/;"
  >
    <a-assets>
      <a-asset-item
        id="glb"
        src="resources/model/untitled-processed.glb"
      ></a-asset-item>
    </a-assets>

    <a-marker
      type="pattern"
      preset="custom"
      url="resources/patterns/bundan_marker.patt"
    >
      <a-entity gltf-model="#glb"></a-entity>
    </a-marker>
    <a-entity camera></a-entity>
  </a-scene>
</template>

<script>
export default {
  name: "Model",
  beforeRouteLeave(to, from, next) {
    next();
    location.reload();
  },
  methods: {
    goBack() {
      this.$router.push("/category");
    },
    find() {
      console.log("marker found du");
    },
    lost() {
      console.log("marker lost");
    },
  },
};
</script>
